Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:17.05,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Titulky od GAW-Subs\Nwww.gawsubs.com
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:16.36,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Si si istá, že budeš v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.49,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Môj domov je tu neďaleko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:23.99,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale nebolo by lepšie, ak by si počkala v škole?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:27.37,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Idem ich pohľadať.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.51,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nemôźem ísť domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.01,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Sama nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:46.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama a otec budú smutní, ak sa vrátim bez Yuukiho..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.41,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo musel Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.09,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vlastne, ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.88,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,som zomrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.60,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.78,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poďme domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.92,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:07.30,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Už nie si, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:13.39,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale si tak zlatý a vraciaš sa ku mne,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:17.90,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,aby som nezostala smutná, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:29.24,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Chcem byť s tebou, {\i1}sestrička.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:32.75,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A chcem, aby sme išli domov spolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.33,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:40.38,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poďme domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:54.52,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dostanem ťa domov, nech sa deje čokoľvek. Počuješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:56.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.58,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pozri, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:10.99,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To je náš dom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:11.91,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.38,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama môže byť doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:20.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:25.17,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:39.23,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.73,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.37,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.28,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.71,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sestrička.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.64,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.14,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:24.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.03,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Odchádzaš preč?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.82,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Ja nikam nejdem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.82,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čo si to povedal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:35.79,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vždy budem pri tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.79,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.25,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nepočujem ťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:43.42,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ja ťa nepočujem, Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.34,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nechoď.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:52.09,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Ľúbim ťa, {\i1}sestrička.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.52,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.56,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.03,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.24,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:17.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.60,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.57,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Som uchvátený, Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.99,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Muselo to byť ťažké.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.12,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vďakabohu, že si nažive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.70,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale Yuuki to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.71,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáč, ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.71,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To nie je tvoja chyba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.75,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mýlila som sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:11.22,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nemala som vás dvoch pustiť samých.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:12.80,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:19.52,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Začala som sa s tebou hádať a tak Yuuki chcel, aby sme...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:21.77,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:31.24,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem, že si zostala pri Yuukim až do konca.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:36.70,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki ma neopustil ani na minútu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bol pri mne až dokiaľ som neprišla domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:43.37,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Bol pri mne, aby som nebola smutná;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.25,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,aby som sa neprestala pokúšať;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.58,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,aby som sa konečne dostala domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:54.13,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dostala som sa sem iba vďaka Yuukimu, ktorý bol pri mne až do konca.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.63,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je to len a len vďaka nemu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:09:04.48,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki mi hovoril, aby som sa s vami viacej rozprávala, keď sa vrátime
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:08.65,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,a že by sme mali ísť do Odaiby a za dedkom, keď sa dostaneme domov...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:13.07,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Chcel toľko toho vidieť...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:20.03,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Stále dookola mi vravel, aby sme išli po moste Rainbow ako rodina, držiac sa za ruky,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.16,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,stále ma povzbudzoval slovami: "poďme domov..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.62,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.08,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.42,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.84,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.26,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:09.79,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Kde je Mirai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:14.00,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nemohla som ju dostať z postele.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.09,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.65,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.79,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nakreslil som žabku, {\i1}sestrička.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:28.58,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že by si mala aj ty s tým už prestať.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:37.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.13,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Raňajky sú hotové. {Raňajky alebo obed - why not have both?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.80,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poďme sa najesť spolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.59,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:49.14,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uplynul jeden mesiac po zemetrasení,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:52.73,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}a mesto sa pomaly vracia do pôvodného stavu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.73,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Daj si trocha šalátu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.69,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:56.73,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Avšak mnohé budovy ešte stále nie sú stabilné,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:58.65,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ale miestne úrady sa snažia o skorú ná—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:21.42,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Viem, že toho na nás bolo veľmi veľa, ale už je skoro koniec Augusta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:30.77,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno, hneď tam budem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.98,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Zdravím, moje meno je Kusakabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.91,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vy musíte byť Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.70,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:51.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte; chcela som vás navštíviť o mnoho skoršie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.46,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale nie, to my by sme sa mali ospravedlniť.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.67,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ďakujeme, že ste si urobili tú námahu a prišili.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Som si istá, že bude rada, keď vás uvidí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:02.42,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tak, kde je Mirai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.43,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.60,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.85,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dosť si schudla.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.40,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.73,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Jem pravidelne a nič nevynechávam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.61,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vonku je tak pekne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:31.79,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je to trochu divný pocit, keď je vonku takto, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.83,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Slnko vychádza a potom zapadá,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:37.04,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,všetci sú plní energie...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Na chvíľu vypadneš z reality, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:49.05,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tak som sa aspoň cítila ja, keď môj manžel zomrel pred mojimi očami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:52.22,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Na pohreb si vôbec nespomínam;
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Naozaj ma udivuje, že som vládala vôbec dýchať.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:14:00.77,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale Hina rástla a rástla každým dňom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:04.03,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Začala sa najprv smiať, neskôr rozprávať,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.74,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,a keď si kýchne, pripomína mi to môjho manžela....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:11.99,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ty a Yuuki ste si veľmi podobní.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:15.25,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,My a podobní?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.04,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:22.00,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki žije naďalej v tebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:24.71,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.34,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tu máš.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.65,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A tiež,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.19,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,toto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.74,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáč, že to tak dlho trvalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:52.24,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Myslela som, že som ho zahodila...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:57.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki ho zodvihol a ochraňoval ho pre teba.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:28.78,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Takže Yuka {\i1}bola{\i0} v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:32.57,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.53,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mám jednu správu od teba, Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:39.29,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.13,M8-Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Drahá {\i1}sestrička.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.50,M8-Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Zdvihol som ti telefón.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:51.09,M8-Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Myslel som si, že by si bez neho bola smutná, keďže si závisláčka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.64,M8-Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Aj ja chcem tiež telefón.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:58.01,M8-Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Mohli by sme si potom písať.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:02.39,M8-Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Tak by sme mohli byť spolu aj keby sme neboli pri sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.86,M8-Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Oh, a tiež chcem robiť fotky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:10.03,M8-Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Poďme rýchlo domov, dajme mame darček a odfoťme sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:15.16,M8-Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Snažme sa ako najlepšie vieme, dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.70,M8-Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Od Yuukiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.16,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.88,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki sa naozaj snažil, všakže?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:31.63,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hlava ho musela ukrutne bolieť celú tu dobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:33.88,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:36.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Celú dobu mu bolo zle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale aj tak kráčal ďalej bez stonania.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:40.18,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:45.94,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pri jedle je dosť prieberčivý,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:48.52,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,ale aj tak zjedol všetko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.36,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Naozaj bol dobré dieťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:51.69,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:55.66,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dal tomu všetko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:56.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:02.54,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čo mám robiť, teraz, keď je Yuuki preč?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:06.21,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Veľmi mi chýba!
Comment: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.21,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.38,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Zavoláme Mirai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:21.52,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Sľúbila Mari, že sa budú obe usmievať, keď sa stretnú nabudúce, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.69,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,vyzerá to tak, že bude potrebovať viacej času.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.52,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A ty to tiež nepreháňaj, dobre, mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.61,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ty tiež, oco.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.11,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Si už hladná?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:40.03,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Alebo by si chcela niečo na pitie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.08,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.75,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Viem, že je trochu neskoro,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.37,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,ale všetko najlepšie k narodeninám.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.46,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vybral to pre teba Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:53.05,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vybral ho preto, lebo máš rada kvetiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:03.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A tiež toto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.48,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je tam napísané  "Pre mamu, od Yuukiho."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:14.65,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pozri sa na to, otec.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:15.86,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.45,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Teba a Mirai nakreslil perfektne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.91,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Naozaj sa mu to podarilo ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:21.78,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:24.20,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Naozaj vyzerám takto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:25.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Drahý Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:30.75,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Náš dom je plný spomienok na teba,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.05,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,takže nech sa deje čokoľvek,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.72,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,stále na teba myslím.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:43.35,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Som si istá, že budem smutná... a bude to bolieť.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:49.23,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale keď to nebudem už zvládať,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.36,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,prídem sa s tebou takto porozprávať.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:57.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poviem ti všetky dobré a vtipné veci, ktoré sa mi stali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.11,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Budeš vedieť o všetkom, čo sa tu deje.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:05.12,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.79,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem, že si mi bol bračekom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.40,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Budem silná, pretože viem, že
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.90,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki na mňa dáva pozor.
